aboutWTMProgram: This I/O season, embrace the power of Kotlin through hands-on sessions followed by 18 hours long hackathon. If you are new to Tensorflow or Kotlin and want to experience the power of a cross-platform, statically typed, general-purpose programming language, or want to dive deeper into machine learning, then you are at the right place.
